subtitleNullable: Fitness App data collected for analysis!
descriptionNullable:
Disclaimer: I dont own this dataset nor did I collect it.
I got this dataset from Coursera and I did a capstone Project on it.
This dataset is from a mobile App called Bellabeat which is a fitness based app. The data has been collected with consent from 30 app users for analysis purposes.
These tables have data like The number of steps taken by people, total distance coveredm total calories they burnt etc.
You can use this dataset to find out if people are losing weight or not, if there is any correlation between variables or not.
Lots of things to figure out, lots of insights can be drawn.
